  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalao de xcb-proto</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>xcb-proto</application> executando os seguintes
comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>PYTHON=python3 ./configure $XORG_CONFIG</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Para testar os resultados, emita: <command>make check</command>.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      If you are upgrading from version 1.15.1 or lower, the old pkgconfig file
needs to be removed. Issue, as the <systemitem
class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="nodump"><userinput>rm -f $XORG_PREFIX/lib/pkgconfig/xcb-proto.pc</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

